666
00:43:32,220 --> 00:43:34,290
Čo? Bodol ducha?

667
00:43:34,680 --> 00:43:35,900
Ducha?

668
00:43:38,450 --> 00:43:41,880
<i>3.júla v Yeonjoo nemocnici,
